Insert at cursor
Performance Pitfalls
❌ N+1 queries in loops
   → for (const user of users) { await getOrg(user.orgId) }
   → Use Prisma include or batch queries

❌ No pagination on list endpoints
   → Returning 10,000 records crashes the app
   → Always paginate: default limit 20, max 100

❌ No DB indexes on foreign keys
   → Every organizationId, userId, status field needs an index
   → Prisma @@index([organizationId]) on every model

❌ Blocking the event loop with sync operations
   → Never use fs.readFileSync, crypto.pbkdfSync in request handlers
   → Use async versions always

❌ No query timeout
   → Slow DB query blocks all requests
   → Set statement_timeout in PostgreSQL connection

