Frontend Pitfalls
❌ Storing sensitive data in localStorage
   → Access tokens in localStorage = XSS vulnerable
   → Use httpOnly cookies for refresh tokens
   → Access tokens in memory or localStorage (short-lived = acceptable)

❌ No loading states
   → User clicks button twice = double submission
   → Always disable buttons during mutation isPending

❌ No error boundaries
   → One component crash = blank white page
   → Wrap feature sections in ErrorBoundary

❌ Fetching data in useEffect
   → Race conditions, no caching, no deduplication
   → Always use TanStack Query

❌ Hydration mismatches
   → Reading localStorage/window on server = hydration error
   → Use useEffect or mounted state guard for client-only reads

